WEBVTT

00:00:00.383 --> 00:00:03.718
er hot nisht gevolt me zol im nemen tsu di arbet.

00:00:02.762 --> 00:00:03.620
yo.

00:00:03.620 --> 00:00:07.043
shpeter hot men genumen di ale mentshn

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:08.949
vos zenen antlofn

00:00:09.107 --> 00:00:11.683
hot men zey genumen tsu a STRAF kolonye

00:00:12.668 --> 00:00:17.775
veyst vos dos heyst a STRAF kolonye? shlepn, hakn berger

00:00:18.253 --> 00:00:23.193
mit di hent, mit di hakn, hak- un shlepn fun eyn plats oyf di andern

00:00:23.193 --> 00:00:25.943
un mit dem hot men zey gemakht di gasn dort

00:00:25.943 --> 00:00:28.094
di geslekh vos m'iz geganen.

00:00:28.094 --> 00:00:32.304
dos iz gevezn shteyner, poshet berger gevezn, matseyves.

00:00:32.304 --> 00:00:36.514
ot dort gevezn a CMIENTARZ, iz dort gevezn a mitsraim iz dort gevezn.

00:00:36.514 --> 00:00:39.611
di plats vos iz di PLASZOW iz gevezn in PODGORZEr

00:00:40.309 --> 00:00:46.347
besoylem iz dort gevezn, hot men gehakt di shteyner, un shteyner fun berg hot men geha-

00:00:46.347 --> 00:00:53.820
un er hot dort gearbet, un dos hot er geshlept oyf aza vegele hin un tsurik, un der yeke iz geshtanen mitn ⟨rayt baytsh⟩ un geshlogn

00:00:54.028 --> 00:00:57.662
vos undz ho'mir gekrign dos bisele broyt hot men im getrogn

00:00:57.662 --> 00:00:58.320
zol

00:00:58.320 --> 00:01:02.240
zol kenen a bisl shtarker zayn, vayl undz ho'mir dokh nisht azoy shver gearbet.

00:01:02.348 --> 00:01:04.142
hot men im getrogn dos do.

00:01:04.142 --> 00:01:06.724
mayn shvester hot men in tsvishn shoyn

00:01:06.724 --> 00:01:08.063
avekgenumen.

00:01:07.900 --> 00:01:09.868
velkhe shvester iz dos geven?

00:01:08.608 --> 00:01:10.647
di vos voynt yetst in Amerike

00:01:10.647 --> 00:01:11.719
di eltste

00:01:11.719 --> 00:01:14.060
hot men shoyn in tsvishn avekgenumen

00:01:14.060 --> 00:01:16.190
iz zi geforn keyn

00:01:16.190 --> 00:01:18.640
Skarzhisk iz zi geforn

00:01:18.640 --> 00:01:24.243
iz zi geforn keyn Skarzhisk. dos iz gevezn dray lager. lager A., lager B., lager C.

00:01:24.243 --> 00:01:26.726
un dort iz gevezn a a MUNITION fabrik

00:01:26.918 --> 00:01:30.748
un dort iz zi gevezn. shpeter fun dort iz ⟨zi geforn⟩ keyn UNK, iz gevezn a

00:01:30.748 --> 00:01:33.348
a biter, a UNK iz men shoyn dort gevorn.

00:01:32.908 --> 00:01:35.247
ven iz dos geven ven zi iz avek?

00:01:34.444 --> 00:01:37.661
dos iz gevezn JAHRE ts- ts-

00:01:38.173 --> 00:01:40.330
tsvey un fertsik iz zi shoyn avek

00:01:40.330 --> 00:01:41.374
fun undz.

00:01:41.278 --> 00:01:43.854
un ir hot zi nisht mer gezen demolts.

00:01:42.679 --> 00:01:46.453
mer hot zi nisht gezen vi z- biz nokh di krig hot men zi nisht gezen.

00:01:46.138 --> 00:01:49.254
un vos iz geven mit di andere shvester?

00:01:48.467 --> 00:01:51.299
di andere shvester iz vider azoy gevezn.

00:01:51.299 --> 00:01:54.450
azoy vi zi iz aroysgeganen fun dem korb, iz zi geganen tsu dem

00:01:54.450 --> 00:01:58.620
UNK s'iz gevezn a UNK. ⟨dos⟩ gantsn in UNK iz gevezn ⟨bayn im⟩ bahaltn

00:01:58.620 --> 00:02:01.060
a tsayt, kh'veys nisht vi lang. yednfal

00:02:01.174 --> 00:02:04.172
peysekh tsayt iz gekumen tsu undz der goy

00:02:04.532 --> 00:02:11.422
un hot ⟨im⟩ gezogt azoy, hot undz gebrengt UNK rayz. m'hot im gegebn gelt. fun lager hot men gegebn durkh di drotn gelt

00:02:11.422 --> 00:02:13.571
un hot gebrengt undz b- dos do.

00:02:13.645 --> 00:02:21.944
rayz hot er undz gebrengt, un aza kashe, ikh veys nisht vi UNK dos hot geheysn, epes azoy ⟨gelenish⟩. m'hot dos oykhet gegesn, hot er undz gebrengt. eyer hot er undz gebrengt

00:02:21.944 --> 00:02:24.980
un hot er gezogt "her tsu, zi vil nisht blaybn. zi vil avek."

00:02:24.980 --> 00:02:28.330
vu vil zi forn? zen- mayn tate hot gehat a shvester

00:02:28.579 --> 00:02:32.707
⟨Shpire⟩ hot dos geheysn in Bokhnye. zi vil forn tsu di tante.

00:02:32.764 --> 00:02:39.789
iz er geganen, hot er zi gefirt dort tsu di tante, un dort iz zi gevezn di gantse tsayt, biz gevezn der, di geto

00:02:39.789 --> 00:02:44.253
likvidirt di Bokhnye, un di tante hot zikh oykhet bahaltn mit a bunker arayn

00:02:44.253 --> 00:02:45.780
⟨do hob⟩ ikh di gantse foto

00:02:45.780 --> 00:02:48.637
oykhet in a bunker arayn mit di gantse familye

00:02:49.032 --> 00:02:52.884
un m'hot dem g- bunker getrofn, un shpeter hot men dem bunker geha-

00:02:52.884 --> 00:02:53.787
geshosn.

00:02:53.787 --> 00:02:55.303
ale mentshn geshosn.

00:02:55.782 --> 00:02:57.700
ir veyst ven dos iz geven?

00:02:58.212 --> 00:03:02.289
dos iz gevezn demolts ven hot men likvidirt Bokhnye.

00:03:02.953 --> 00:03:06.389
ikh veys genoy, vayl do eyner hot gevoynt in Antverpn

00:03:07.155 --> 00:03:11.384
vos iz gevezn oykhet a kapo, keyn nomen vil ikh nisht zogn, un er hot dos gezen.

00:03:12.353 --> 00:03:16.481
un vos iz gevorn mit aykh dort in PLASZOW vayter?

00:03:15.525 --> 00:03:23.146
⟨un⟩ in PLASZOW iz gevezn, undz ho'mir gearbet demolts. ikh bin gevezn ⟨oyfn⟩ krankn shpitol. shpeter bin ikh gezunt gevorn, hob ikh vayter gearbet.

00:03:23.220 --> 00:03:25.812
shpeter hot men undz genumen

00:03:25.887 --> 00:03:27.551
keyn WIELICKA.

00:03:27.574 --> 00:03:33.474
m'hot gekumen a grupe hot men undz genumen keyn WIELICZKA, hobn mir gearbet dort in WIELICZKA bay zalts grobn

00:03:33.683 --> 00:03:34.742
a tsayt

00:03:34.742 --> 00:03:38.752
shpeter f- s'hot zikh dos likvidirt, ⟨iz⟩ men tsurikgekumen keyn PLASZOW

00:03:38.752 --> 00:03:41.652
hot men vider gearbet banayen

00:03:41.652 --> 00:03:43.683
yekishe mundirn.

00:03:43.960 --> 00:03:47.194
ikh bin gezesn un geneyt yekishe mundirn bay a mashin

00:03:48.212 --> 00:03:51.255
ikh mit mayn shvester tsuzamen oyf dem zelbn plats.

00:03:51.255 --> 00:03:53.319
un az ze'mir geforn keyn

00:03:53.781 --> 00:03:57.167
keyn WIELICZKA, hot men tsun ersht genumen di mame

00:03:58.067 --> 00:04:04.051
hot der tate gezogt "az m'hot di mamen genumen, gey du oykhet." hob ikh mikh tsugeshtelt tsu di mamen ⟨hot⟩ gezogt

00:04:04.125 --> 00:04:05.936
"aleyn vestu nisht blaybn

00:04:05.936 --> 00:04:09.530
un aleyn vestu UNK adurkhlebn di krig. gey tsuzamen."

00:04:09.530 --> 00:04:14.194
un az m'hot genumen mayn shvester keyn Skarzhisk dort

00:04:14.537 --> 00:04:20.533
hot der tate gezogt tsu ⟨ir⟩ "eyne shteln zikh nisht tsu keyn tsvey." hot men oykhet gekent zikh tsushteln

00:04:20.533 --> 00:04:23.829
zogt er "shteln zikh nisht keyn tsvey. me veyst nisht vu me geyt"

00:04:24.207 --> 00:04:30.110
hot er gezogt, un far dem ⟨o⟩ zenen mir geblibn ale lebn azoy. ot azoy, der kop hot im geshpilt biz tsu di letste minut

00:04:30.110 --> 00:04:31.980
vi azoy tsu firn undz.

00:04:33.488 --> 00:04:37.228
un shpeter zenen mir tsurikgekumen keyn PLASZOW, hobn mir vayter gearbet.

00:04:33.638 --> 00:04:34.408
un

00:04:37.302 --> 00:04:40.468
shpeter gevezn di selektsye fun Mengele

00:04:41.622 --> 00:04:51.560
undz ze'mir gevezn. ikh bin geblibn b- vay- vayter gearbet. shpeter hobn zey langzam ongehoybn, iz gekumen fun MAJDANEK iz gekumen di blok ALTESTE di k- di yekishe

00:04:51.560 --> 00:04:56.131
blok ALTESTE zenen gekumen, zenen gevezn azolkhene ⟨reshoim⟩, nisht gevezn di tsveyte.

00:04:56.131 --> 00:04:59.312
eyn mol geyt zi tsu mir, shteyen mir ale oyfn apel plats opge-

00:04:59.312 --> 00:05:02.722
opgeshtelt, un zey UNK geganen. zey hobn undz gerekhnt, di SCHMUCKSTUCK

00:05:02.722 --> 00:05:05.762
UNK s'iz in ordenung, hot zi gezogt

00:05:05.922 --> 00:05:09.792
hot zi gerekhnt. UNK geyt zi tsu mir tsu, get zi mir azoy ONE AND

00:05:09.792 --> 00:05:13.422
TWO fun beyde ⟨zayts⟩ az ikh, mayn kop hot azoy zikh geshoklt.

00:05:13.436 --> 00:05:16.186
kh'hob nisht gevust far vos, far ven, geyt zi mir, patsht zi.

00:05:16.186 --> 00:05:19.722
zi nemt aroys a tashn tikhl, shmirt UNK mayne lipn tsi ikh hob ge-

00:05:19.722 --> 00:05:21.052
mikh opgeshminket.

00:05:21.345 --> 00:05:25.493
ikh hob gehat a lipn ⟨shtif⟩ demo- ikh hob gehat a seykhl ⟨iber hoypt⟩ oyf a lipn ⟨shtif⟩

00:05:25.493 --> 00:05:30.451
zi hot mikh azoy gehakt in beyde zaytn az ikh hob gemeynt az shpeter bin ikh krank gevorn fun dem

00:05:30.947 --> 00:05:32.792
un shoyn, dos iz gevezn.

00:05:32.792 --> 00:05:36.601
un zey hobn gevezn, zey hobn geshlogn geharget di, di yekes

00:05:36.601 --> 00:05:41.721
di yekete vos hot mikh gehakt hot men zi oykhet gebrengt keyn Poyln. m'hot zi geharg- geshosn.

00:05:40.768 --> 00:05:42.854
ir veyst vi zi hot geheysn?

00:05:42.190 --> 00:05:44.371
neyn. a hoykhe a blonde

00:05:44.371 --> 00:05:47.001
UNK eybik getrogn azolkhene pelerine

00:05:47.001 --> 00:05:49.791
unter di pelerine hot zi azoy geharget mentshn

00:05:49.791 --> 00:05:50.751
kh'veys gornisht vi UNK

00:05:50.751 --> 00:05:53.831
⟨iz⟩ demolts hot men moyre gehat tsu kukn oyf a mentsh

00:05:53.831 --> 00:05:55.751
oyf yekes UNK, m'hot dokh b-

00:05:55.751 --> 00:05:58.161
m'hot nor gekukt, zol, zol nisht kukn oyf mir

00:05:58.183 --> 00:06:00.133
vert er mikh ⟨derkukn⟩, vet er mikh shisn

00:06:00.133 --> 00:06:03.353
vos hot men gehat interese mit a yeke tsu kukn? UNK moyre gehat.

00:06:03.516 --> 00:06:08.353
efsher di eltere mentshn hobn gekent di nemen, ABER UNK ver hot gekent ⟨dem⟩ nomen?

00:06:08.359 --> 00:06:10.532
m'hot dokh nisht gekent keyn nomen nebekh ⟨o⟩

00:06:10.532 --> 00:06:14.793
m'hot nisht gekent keyn nomen. m'hot nisht gevust keyn date. m'hot nisht gevust keyn tog

00:06:14.793 --> 00:06:16.263
m'iz geganen bay tog

00:06:16.263 --> 00:06:19.423
aroysge- bay nakht iz men aroysgeganen fun barakn shlofn.

00:06:19.423 --> 00:06:24.093
bay nakht iz men tsurik gekumen in barak arayn shlofn, un dos iz gevezn, a gantsn tog hot men gearbet.

00:06:23.580 --> 00:06:25.751
mentshn zenen geshtorbn dort?

00:06:25.234 --> 00:06:31.120
zikher zenen geshtorbn. zenen geshtorbn, eyner iz geshtorbn fun kelt, un eyner iz geshtorbn vayl zi hot nisht ⟨gekent⟩ mer oyshaltn.

00:06:31.120 --> 00:06:34.745
un azoy zenen zey nebekh avek, un der vos iz avek, hot men gemakht a

00:06:34.920 --> 00:06:37.971
a lokh, un m'hot dos gegebn a, dos do

00:06:37.971 --> 00:06:40.030
v- vos hot men gebrengt UNK

00:06:40.030 --> 00:06:42.677
rebes hot men ne- nebekh gebrengt demolts

00:06:42.683 --> 00:06:44.561
farshidene, di

00:06:44.561 --> 00:06:51.401
dem DZIALOSZYCEr rebn hot men gebrengt keyn Kroke. m'hot gevezn oykhet bahaltn, hot men im oykhet gebrengt, hot men im oykhet geshosn keyn PLASZOW

00:06:51.627 --> 00:06:55.017
vemen az, s'iz geven TERRIBLE, TERRIBLE

00:06:55.017 --> 00:06:56.697
un a sakh galokhim ho-

00:06:56.697 --> 00:07:00.727
hob ikh azoy gehert hot dort oykhet geshosn. zey hobn zey aroyfgebrengt.

00:06:59.693 --> 00:07:01.644
s'iz geven goyishe

00:07:01.347 --> 00:07:05.250
neyn, s- dort bay undz in PLASZOW, oybn oyfn barg, un m'hot gemakht griber

00:07:05.250 --> 00:07:08.057
az di, m'hot likvidirt di geto

00:07:08.333 --> 00:07:14.353
hobn zey, mentshn, gemuzt oyf d- l- der lager, m'hot likvidirt dem lager

00:07:14.353 --> 00:07:19.964
hobn di mentshn gemuzt ⟨oyfkloybn⟩ di greber un farbrenen di ale mentsh, zol nisht blaybn keyn tseykhn

00:07:20.297 --> 00:07:21.506
hot er gemuzt.

00:07:21.276 --> 00:07:24.105
un vi lang zent ir dort geblibn in PLASZOW?

00:07:23.875 --> 00:07:27.058
in PLASZOW bin ikh gevezn biz

00:07:27.418 --> 00:07:29.943
biz fir un fertsik zenen mir gevezn in PLASZOW.

00:07:30.034 --> 00:07:31.378
lange tsayt.

00:07:31.620 --> 00:07:33.082
a sakh mitgemakht.

00:07:33.173 --> 00:07:35.394
un nokh dem, vos iz geven?

00:07:34.472 --> 00:07:36.913
nokh dem zenen mir geforn keyn OSWIECIM.

00:07:36.447 --> 00:07:38.432
ver hot dos bashlosn?

00:07:38.337 --> 00:07:42.701
als di yekes vos UNK gekumen UNK s'iz gekumen un me, m'hot gedarft

00:07:42.876 --> 00:07:46.382
likvidirn vider azoy vi es hot zikh ongehoybn di WA- krig

00:07:46.382 --> 00:07:48.213
di rusn zenen geganen nenter

00:07:48.213 --> 00:07:51.881
hobn zey dokh nisht gevolt hobn azoy fil mentshn do lig- undz zoln mir zayn

00:07:51.887 --> 00:07:54.378
hobn zey geshikt keyn ⟨OSWIECIM⟩, zol men farbrenen

00:07:55.060 --> 00:07:57.824
un dort ot iz gekumen vider a selektstye

00:07:57.824 --> 00:07:59.256
in OSWIECIM

00:07:58.738 --> 00:08:01.708
vos iz, vi azoy iz forgegangen di

00:08:01.708 --> 00:08:05.388
UPRISE fun PLASZOW? vos gedenk ir fun dem?

00:08:04.442 --> 00:08:06.970
oy, demolts iz gevezn a tragedye.

00:08:06.970 --> 00:08:14.156
iz gekumen, zey hobn ⟨tsugenumen, hot men⟩ gemakht a spetsyel barakn oyf eyn zayt, un di ale mentshn vos hot men

00:08:14.331 --> 00:08:18.780
tsuzamgenumen, hot men zey arayngeleygt in di barakn

00:08:19.613 --> 00:08:22.071
un der tate iz yedes mol gekumen

00:08:22.583 --> 00:08:26.477
un hot gebetn zey "antloyfts, antloyfts, antloyfts"

00:08:26.477 --> 00:08:32.060
hot men dokh moyre gehat. vu zol men loyfn? tsurik in lager arayn. m'hot nisht ⟨gegebn⟩ ergets ⟨arayn⟩ UNK tsurik in lager arayn loyfn.

00:08:32.202 --> 00:08:35.183
zogt er "ikh vel kumen. kh'vel nemen a ZANGE

00:08:35.610 --> 00:08:37.380
un ⟨vel⟩ oyfmakhn di

00:08:37.380 --> 00:08:39.650
di drot vos iz gevezn f- arum un arum mit

00:08:39.650 --> 00:08:42.670
keyt mit drerd, ⟨vel⟩ ikh oyfmakhn un antloyfts."

00:08:42.967 --> 00:08:48.193
yednfal, di mame hot moyre gehat. azoy vi zi hot moyre gehat, bin ikh nisht mitgeganen.

00:08:48.250 --> 00:08:51.939
andere mentshn oyf dem plats zenen zey antlofn. undz ze'mir UNK in shtekh

00:08:52.941 --> 00:08:58.321
iz er geganen. oyf di letste minut zogt UNK "⟨ir muzt zikh⟩ geyn bahaltn." vu iz dokh UNK?

00:08:58.321 --> 00:09:00.961
iz gevezn a vash ROOM

00:09:00.961 --> 00:09:05.021
vi azoy iz gevezn di vash ROOM? oybn iz ⟨gevezn⟩ aza groyse plite

00:09:05.021 --> 00:09:12.181
un fun di plite arunter iz gevezn a drot, un do hot gegosn dos vaser vos di mentshn hobn ⟨zikh dos⟩ gevashn. dos iz gevezn di vash ROOM.

00:09:12.432 --> 00:09:21.977
un oyf di plite hot men zikh gegebn a leyg aroyf, aroyfgegangen, eyne ⟨haltn⟩, di tsveyte azoy aroyfgeshprungen oybn oyf di plite. zenen mir azoy dort gelegn, ikh mit mayn mame

00:09:23.215 --> 00:09:25.375
oyf letst ban aroysforn

00:09:25.375 --> 00:09:28.395
hobn zey dokh gezen az s'felt tsvey m- ts- mentshn

00:09:28.648 --> 00:09:31.932
zenen gekumen zukhn. zey hobn iberal gezukht

00:09:31.939 --> 00:09:35.488
iz gekumen tsum WASCHRAUM, iz gekumen a O.D. vider dos zelbe

00:09:35.488 --> 00:09:37.091
iz gekumen a O.D.

00:09:37.091 --> 00:09:38.154
un zogt er

00:09:38.154 --> 00:09:46.372
hot er zikh anidergeshtelt oybn, hot er undz gezen lign. "geyts arunter, geyts arunter." zog ikh "neyn, undz geyen mir nisht arunter. gey aroys, ⟨zogt⟩ az d'host undz nisht gezen."

00:09:46.372 --> 00:09:50.751
"neyn, geyts arunter. vest nisht aropgeyn, vel ikh rufn a S.S. man." iz er geganen

00:09:50.751 --> 00:09:52.655
hot gerufn di S.S. manke

00:09:52.965 --> 00:10:00.620
un az undz ho'mir shoyn gezen di S.S. manke, hobn mir shoyn gegebn a shpring arop. di mame iz geven nebekh di ershte. zi hot tsuge- nebekh gekrign klep

00:10:00.728 --> 00:10:03.506
un ikh hob gegebn shnel a shpring arunter un gelofn

00:10:03.580 --> 00:10:04.991
tsum transport

00:10:06.229 --> 00:10:08.361
ze'mir dort geforn keyn OSWIECIM.

00:10:08.361 --> 00:10:10.628
ze'mir gekumen keyn OSWIECIM

00:10:09.823 --> 00:10:12.916
vifl mentshn zenen geforn oyf ayer transport?

00:10:12.916 --> 00:10:14.812
s'iz geven a groyser transport?

00:10:14.717 --> 00:10:19.891
a finef toyznt mentshn zenen geforn, finef toyznt. in yedn vagon iz gevezn efsher

00:10:19.982 --> 00:10:26.861
a vagon, aza farmakhte vagon, un in di vagon hot men arayngeshtupt efsher hundert tsvo- tsvey hundert mentshn, ikh hob nisht keyn UNK

00:10:26.935 --> 00:10:31.029
un s'iz gevezn aza kleyn fentsterl mit ⟨ayzernes⟩.

00:10:31.137 --> 00:10:33.108
mayn mame hot zikh anidergeshtelt

00:10:33.108 --> 00:10:34.466
bay di ⟨ayzernes⟩

00:10:34.466 --> 00:10:38.488
un iz geshtanen a S.S. man dort dernebn. zogt zi "ikh hob do a kind

00:10:38.815 --> 00:10:40.884
un zi darf a bisele vaser"

00:10:41.245 --> 00:10:42.994
zogt er "KOMM NACH VORNE"

00:10:43.033 --> 00:10:44.799
un ikh kum NACH VORNE.

00:10:44.822 --> 00:10:48.641
er hot oyfgemakht di tir. s'iz gevezn di tirn tsugemakht

00:10:48.641 --> 00:10:55.678
un ikh hob mikh anidergezetst mit di mame. "zets dikh do anidert" hot er mir gezogt, un ikh hob mir anidergezetst mit di mame, un er hot mir gegebn vaser.

00:10:55.678 --> 00:10:59.129
er iz gevezn nisht keyn mentsh nor UNK malekh iz er gevezn.

00:10:59.129 --> 00:11:02.738
er hot undz ale fartsaygt vos tut zikh in OSWIECIM.

00:11:02.777 --> 00:11:04.450
ir hot dos gevust?

00:11:03.925 --> 00:11:07.091
er hot shoyn gevust, vayl er hot gefirt di transportn hin un tsurik.

00:11:07.114 --> 00:11:09.904
er iz gekumen fun yedn plats tsu forn hin un tsurik.

00:11:09.904 --> 00:11:12.679
hot er undz gezogt "az vest kumen keyn OSWIECIM

00:11:12.679 --> 00:11:20.304
afile vestu geyn, vest visn az zey zogn az zey geyen tsu di arbet, zey geyen vayter in krematoryum. zolst dikh g- yedes mol bahaltn."

00:11:20.428 --> 00:11:23.741
dos iz gevezn poshet a malekh vos er hot ⟨dos undz⟩ UNK oyfgefirt.

00:11:23.741 --> 00:11:26.767
hot undz alts gezogt. s'iz gekumen a transport keyn STUTTHOF

00:11:27.313 --> 00:11:31.070
ales iz geganen, dos iz, hot men gevorfn, zenen ale mentshn in vaser arayn.

00:11:31.228 --> 00:11:35.528
in STUTTHOF iz gevezn a vaser. m'hot ale mentshn lebedikerheyt arayngevorfn in vaser.

00:11:35.528 --> 00:11:37.348
undz ze'mir nisht dort gevezn.

00:11:37.354 --> 00:11:38.360
m'hot geshikt

00:11:38.569 --> 00:11:40.219
andere transportn.

00:11:40.219 --> 00:11:43.799
undz ze'mir nisht geven. yedes mol hot men zikh bahaltn. vos heyst bahaltn?

00:11:43.799 --> 00:11:45.689
m'hot genumen a por blokn

00:11:45.689 --> 00:11:49.920
un UNK gey. un azoy vi hot men genumen dem blok, m'iz gelofn vayter.

00:11:50.466 --> 00:11:54.386
farshteyst? dos iz gevezn bahaltn, hot men zikh gegangen tsu ⟨bahaltn⟩ nor antloyfn a bisl vayt.

00:11:54.386 --> 00:11:57.867
eyn mol iz gevezn, dos iz dos letste mol iz gevezn

00:11:58.195 --> 00:12:05.288
hot, shpeter az undz ho'mir gehat tsurikshteln tsu dem tran- tsu undzer blok, hot er gezen az s'iz geblibn finef zeks mentshn vos zey hobn zikh bahaltn

00:12:05.288 --> 00:12:09.253
hot men undz genumen NACH VORNE bay di S.S. manen, zogn az di mentshn g-

00:12:09.253 --> 00:12:12.965
hobn mir undz geknit fir un tsvontsik shtundn

00:12:12.965 --> 00:12:14.355
oyf di fis

00:12:14.682 --> 00:12:20.028
nisht gegesn, nisht gor- nor geknit oyf di fis fir un tsvontsik shtundn far dem UNK a shtrof

00:12:20.028 --> 00:12:22.117
az ze'mir nisht geganen tsum transport.

00:12:23.929 --> 00:12:29.002
lomir tsurikgeyn nokh tsu di rayze. vi lang iz geven di rayze keyn Oyshvits?

00:12:27.844 --> 00:12:30.487
di rayze iz gevezn tsvey vokhn.

00:12:30.814 --> 00:12:34.352
m'iz azoy gez- nisht keyn vaser, nisht keyn esn, nisht gor-

00:12:33.885 --> 00:12:36.427
m'hot zikh opgeshtelt a mol?

00:12:35.556 --> 00:12:41.861
yo. zey hobn zikh opgeshtelt, vayl di yekes hobn zikh ⟨makh fray⟩ vaser ge- getrunken un gegesn

00:12:38.391 --> 00:12:39.330
me

00:12:40.028 --> 00:12:42.519
m'hot oyfgemakht

00:12:42.103 --> 00:12:46.923
far undz hot men gornisht gegebn. er hot nor mir gebrengt dos vaser far mir, dos iz gevezn.

00:12:46.542 --> 00:12:49.742
un mentshn zenen geshtorbn dort?

00:12:47.773 --> 00:12:51.175
geshtorbn vi di fliges. un s'iz gevezn AUGUSTUS.

00:12:51.486 --> 00:12:53.910
dos iz gevezn di greste hits in Poyln.

00:12:53.983 --> 00:12:56.528
un mentshn hobn zikh mitgenumen epes?

00:12:56.413 --> 00:12:59.463
m'hot zikh gornisht mitgenumen. m'hot dokh gornisht gehat mittsunemen.

00:12:59.463 --> 00:13:01.523
m'hot zikh gekent mitnemen a UNK

00:13:01.523 --> 00:13:06.260
keyn flash hot men nisht gehat. vos hostu gekent mitnemen? host dokh gornisht gekent mitnemen. m'iz azoy geganen.

00:13:05.813 --> 00:13:08.642
un m'hot gevust v- tsu vos me geyt?

00:13:08.900 --> 00:13:11.544
m'hot yo gevust un m'hot nisht gevust.

00:13:11.544 --> 00:13:14.834
m'hot gevust az me geyt oyf a transport. m'hot shoyn gevust iz shoyn biter.

00:13:15.162 --> 00:13:20.710
m'hot shoyn gevust iz shoyn biter. m'hot shoyn gehert fun dem. m'hot shoyn gevust az s'iz shoyn biter, vayl mentshn zenen gekumen tsu loyfn

00:13:20.710 --> 00:13:24.724
vos zenen antlofn vos zey hobn shoyn gekumen tsu loyfn, az OSWIECIM iz biter.

00:13:25.303 --> 00:13:30.362
un der yeke hot gezogt az mir geyen mir keyn OSWIECIM. mayn mame hot zikh oykhet gebetn, "loy- antloyf."

00:13:30.362 --> 00:13:33.228
zog ikh "mame, vu ⟨vel⟩ ikh geyn? ikh hob dokh nisht vu tsu geyn.

00:13:33.437 --> 00:13:37.889
kh'hob nisht vu tsu geyn. tsu velkhe goye zol ikh geyn? UNK tsvey dray tog vet zi mikh avekshikn."

00:13:37.889 --> 00:13:41.699
eyn mol bin ikh gevezn a- avekgeshikt in a dorf arayn bay a goye

00:13:42.432 --> 00:13:48.140
vos der tate hot ir gegebn a sakh gelt, iz zi gekumen mikh UNK keyn, in geto arayn, un m'hot mikh avekgefirt

00:13:48.140 --> 00:13:50.351
bin ikh gevezn dort a tsvey vokhn.

00:13:50.351 --> 00:13:56.611
dos vos hob ikh geribn di fis UNK un gesheylt di kartofl un UNK iz gevezn alts tsu veynik

00:13:56.611 --> 00:14:02.720
un a stodole hob ikh gevashn un ale hob ikh ⟨getun⟩. stodole heyst vu di khayes zenen. dos heyst a stodole.

00:14:02.720 --> 00:14:06.129
UNK nokh alts gevezn ⟨tsu heym⟩. UNK hot zi mikh gegebn a shik aroys

00:14:06.129 --> 00:14:08.447
oyf a feld mit tsvey kuen

00:14:09.145 --> 00:14:12.425
un azoy vi zi hot mikh a shik aroys gegebn mit di tsvey kuen, hot zi mir gezogt

00:14:12.425 --> 00:14:13.735
"zolstu geyn

00:14:14.022 --> 00:14:19.233
halt zi bay di shtrik, un zolstu geyn, zolstu zi nisht ⟨nokhlozn⟩." ikh hob zi takesh nisht nokhgelozt

00:14:19.233 --> 00:14:24.376
nor eyn mol bin ikh geganen fun untn. do iz gevezn di shtrik, un do fun hintn

00:14:24.400 --> 00:14:26.048
a ku iz zeyer klug

00:14:26.560 --> 00:14:33.118
hot zi gezen az ikh bin aruntergegangen. ikh bin gevezn a fremde. zi hot mikh nisht gekent. a ku ⟨er⟩ zet nisht a fremde iz azoy vi a hunt

00:14:33.377 --> 00:14:36.245
hot zi gegebn a shpring aroyf mit, mit di fis, un di sh-

00:14:36.245 --> 00:14:39.305
di shtrik iz antlofn. ikh bin gegebn a fal

00:14:39.305 --> 00:14:41.151
un dort gevezn andere

00:14:41.494 --> 00:14:46.500
kinder goyim, hobn zey shoyn gezen s'iz a yidishe, vayl velkher goy ken nisht pashn a ku?

00:14:46.708 --> 00:14:50.229
az, iz zenen shoyn gekumen tsu ir tsu geyn tsu eltern

00:14:50.505 --> 00:14:53.283
un zey hobn gezogt "her tsu, du haltst a yidishe.

00:14:53.357 --> 00:14:54.653
zolstu visn

00:14:54.653 --> 00:15:02.683
az undz veln mir ale d- geyn, zey veln undz ale shisn." azoy hobn gezogt di yekes, az vet men trefn a yidishe, vet men ale shisn. iz geganen dem andern tog, hot zi mir tsurikgefirt in geto arayn.

00:15:04.258 --> 00:15:07.723
ir zent ongekumen keyn Oyshvits nokh

00:15:07.667 --> 00:15:10.445
undz ze'mir ongekumen keyn OSWIECIM

00:15:09.422 --> 00:15:12.555
ven iz dos geven?

00:15:11.295 --> 00:15:13.381
AUGUSTUS, for ⟨di⟩ yontoyvim

00:15:13.303 --> 00:15:15.119
velkhe JAHR veystu nokh?

00:15:14.738 --> 00:15:17.415
dos iz gevezn fir un fertsik.

00:15:17.758 --> 00:15:21.701
un vos hot ir gezen di ershte zakh vos m'hot gezen?

00:15:20.222 --> 00:15:23.658
di ershte zakh, zenen mir gekumen, shoyn vider geshtanen Mengele

00:15:24.492 --> 00:15:30.426
un es hot shoyn vider ⟨sekretirt⟩ vider der oyf links, der oyf rekhts, der oyf links, d- nakedikerheyt.

00:15:30.887 --> 00:15:32.619
oysgetun di kleyder

00:15:32.642 --> 00:15:35.218
un nakedikerheyt, azoy zenen mir geganen.

00:15:35.781 --> 00:15:38.140
got zay dank, undz ze'mir UNK oyf rekhts.

00:15:38.140 --> 00:15:39.606
nisht gegan oyf links.

00:15:39.662 --> 00:15:46.828
s'hot gedoyert a gantsn tog biz d- azoy fil mentshn zenen arayngeganen in di b- m'hot zikh gevashn

00:15:47.712 --> 00:15:50.105
un shpeter hobn zey undz gegebn di ⟨pashakn⟩

00:15:50.105 --> 00:15:55.063
shpeter hot men undz geshoyrn di hor, un iberal vu hobn mir geh- -hat hor, hot men alts opgeshoyrn

00:15:55.221 --> 00:15:57.082
zenen mir aroysgeganen vi a man

00:15:57.082 --> 00:15:58.640
komplet on a hor

00:15:59.490 --> 00:16:00.389
un

00:16:00.389 --> 00:16:03.639
dos hot gedoyert a gantsn tog. zey ⟨veln⟩ zikh fregn far hob ikh ge-

00:16:03.639 --> 00:16:10.039
gedoyert a gantsn tog? nisht durkh dem az undz ze'mir nisht gevezn in di reye, nor der yeke hot gezogt zoln mir nisht geyn, zenen mir antlofn

00:16:11.050 --> 00:16:13.173
hot er gezogt der daytsh, der S.S. man.

00:16:13.173 --> 00:16:16.798
hobn mir gekukt vi azoy antloyfn. m'hot nisht gehat vuhin tsu antloyfn

00:16:17.479 --> 00:16:25.421
hobn mir geshtanen a gantsn tog. gevezn di flesher, un do gevezn shmuts. der hot gebrokhn, der ahin. m'hot zikh azoy g- oyf dem plats gedreyt ahin un tsurik

00:16:25.461 --> 00:16:30.635
un di flign gevezn, hobn gebisn, nisht gevezn tsu- oystsuhaltn, vayl s'iz gevezn AUGUSTUS

00:16:31.198 --> 00:16:39.106
un yednfal, bay nakht zenen mir arayngegangen dokh in di ⟨zal⟩ UNK. m'hot undz dokh geshoyrn, un shpeter hot men undz tsugefirt in a barak arayn. m'hot undz gegebn

00:16:39.349 --> 00:16:41.452
m'hot UNK gegebn a la- a

00:16:41.914 --> 00:16:45.319
a ts- a bluzke, a bluz, hot men gegebn mit a rok

00:16:45.319 --> 00:16:47.918
nisht keyn untervesh, gornisht.

00:16:47.918 --> 00:16:51.290
di ⟨pashakn⟩ hobn zey undz oysgetun, un dos hot men undz gegebn.

00:16:50.402 --> 00:16:51.999
vos heyst ⟨pashakn⟩?

00:16:51.837 --> 00:16:56.069
dos iz aza kleyd mit pasn, vayl dos hobn mir gehat in

00:16:56.069 --> 00:16:59.992
PLASZOW, azolkhene pasn, hobn zey dokh gevolt dos zoyber makhn, oysvashn

00:16:59.992 --> 00:17:01.989
hot men undz dos alts tsugenumen

00:17:02.063 --> 00:17:05.668
un yeder eyner, vos er hot gebrengt, hot gemuzt lozn lign.

00:17:06.467 --> 00:17:10.167
undz ze'mir adurkhgeganen in di ⟨SAUM⟩ kolonye, un shpeter

00:17:10.167 --> 00:17:14.567
hot men undz hintn arum, andere zayt aroysgegan, opgeshoyrn fun oybn aroys

00:17:14.606 --> 00:17:16.500
on a gornisht oyfn kop

00:17:16.693 --> 00:17:18.391
un azoy ze'mir geganen.

00:17:17.892 --> 00:17:20.400
ir hot gehat, hot bakumen a numer?

00:17:20.386 --> 00:17:21.867
yo. ikh hob a numer.

00:17:21.925 --> 00:17:26.154
akht hun-, akhtsn, akhtsn toyznt zeks hundert finef un zibetsik.

00:17:25.214 --> 00:17:26.760
ken men dos zen?

00:17:27.003 --> 00:17:28.195
UNK

00:17:33.045 --> 00:17:35.536
dos hot ir bakumen in Oyshvits?

00:17:34.817 --> 00:17:38.490
dos hob ikh gekrign in UNK dem nomen. azoy vi ze'mir gekumen

00:17:38.547 --> 00:17:41.021
undz g- ikh bin gevezn in A. lager

00:17:41.331 --> 00:17:45.273
un azoy vi bin ikh gekumen, hot er undz bald ale tatuirt.

00:17:45.634 --> 00:17:47.585
dos iz, dos geyt mit a INK

00:17:47.794 --> 00:17:49.020
s'gist arayn

00:17:49.228 --> 00:17:51.466
es gist arayn d- dos do.

00:17:52.131 --> 00:17:54.082
nu, tomer s'iz shver es

00:17:54.257 --> 00:17:55.837
ikh hob ⟨mir alts in⟩ langzam

00:17:56.012 --> 00:17:58.453
un ze'mir ganen in a barak arayn

00:17:58.881 --> 00:18:02.047
un dort in barak hot men shoyn gekrign a

00:18:02.121 --> 00:18:06.924
a kots, a deke, un dos iz gevezn on a, on a shtroy

00:18:07.032 --> 00:18:10.538
oykh on a gornisht, on a shtroy, on a gornisht

00:18:10.538 --> 00:18:12.614
hobn mir gelegn oyf di barakn

00:18:12.614 --> 00:18:15.817
iz gevezn yede pritshe mit finef mentshn.

00:18:15.975 --> 00:18:18.233
mit finef mentshn ⟨in⟩ yede pritshe

00:18:18.233 --> 00:18:19.833
un azoy iz men geshlofn.

00:18:20.717 --> 00:18:25.351
un vifl kinder neb- yeder iz gevezn nokh nebekh zeyer kri- hungerik

00:18:25.780 --> 00:18:29.250
un m'hot zikh gemuzt. m'hot ⟨ongegebn⟩ dos fertl shtikele broyt

00:18:29.250 --> 00:18:31.460
tsvey hundert fuftsik gram broyt, oyf

00:18:31.460 --> 00:18:33.100
haynt in di fri

00:18:33.100 --> 00:18:35.920
un oyf bay nakht, un mitog hobn zey gekrign a zup.

00:18:36.833 --> 00:18:43.526
un eyn mol hot men zikh bahaltn. m'hot zikh geteylt mit di mame. eyn fertl hot men oyfgegesn. dos tsveyte fertl

00:18:43.566 --> 00:18:46.175
hot men bahaltn zikh unter kop.

00:18:46.283 --> 00:18:49.005
keyn kishn hot men nisht gehat, nor azoy untern kop.

00:18:49.005 --> 00:18:53.870
oyf eyn mol get ⟨JEMAND⟩ a shprung adurkh. s'iz gevezn aza groyse lange oyvn

00:18:54.552 --> 00:18:59.248
fun tsigl gemakht. fun eyn zayt arayn⟨UNK⟩ UNK tsvey. iz gegebn a shprung aroys ⟨JEMAND⟩

00:18:59.248 --> 00:19:04.957
un m'hot mir aroyfgekhapt dos shtikele broyt. ikh bin nokh geshprungen, ABER ikh hob shoyn nisht ⟨JEMAND⟩ nebekh getrofn.

00:19:05.503 --> 00:19:08.079
bin gevezn shoyn on a broyt a gantsn tog.

00:19:08.170 --> 00:19:09.767
nor mit di bisele zup.

00:19:09.823 --> 00:19:15.453
un ir hot dort getrofn mentshn, andere mentshn fun WARSCHA- fun KRAKOW?

00:19:14.633 --> 00:19:19.740
yo. dort gevezn zeyer a sakh mentshn. zeyer a sakh mentshn gevezn dort UNK.

00:19:18.362 --> 00:19:21.326
nu vos hot men dort gezogt vos tut zikh?

00:19:19.982 --> 00:19:26.391
gornisht, iz g- m'hot dokh gezen ⟨di, di⟩ roykh. m'hot shoyn gezen. der roykh brent bay nakht un bay tog. di

00:19:26.391 --> 00:19:29.442
di gantse himl iz gevezn royt mit fayer

00:19:29.854 --> 00:19:33.454
host aroysgege- vayl di barakn iz gev- nisht gevezn keyn fentster.

00:19:33.454 --> 00:19:35.467
nor oybn oyf di barakn

00:19:35.490 --> 00:19:41.238
iz gevezn gemakht azolkhene gloz shtiklekh, un durkh dem gloz bay nakht hot men gezen dos fayer

00:19:41.329 --> 00:19:42.085
b-

00:19:42.085 --> 00:19:43.281
brent.

00:19:43.168 --> 00:19:47.077
v- vos hot men aykh gezogt? m'hot aykh gezogt vos dos iz?

00:19:46.476 --> 00:19:53.507
m'hot UNK gevust UNK shoyn di kapos hobn shoyn gevust, vayl di kapos zenen shoyn dort gevezn fun frier, nisht UNK letstn gekumen.

00:19:53.445 --> 00:19:55.633
ver zenen di kapos geven?

00:19:55.133 --> 00:19:57.877
di yidn zenen gevezn di kapos, fun Tshekhn.

00:19:58.288 --> 00:20:00.509
zey zenen nokh frier leyder gekumen

00:20:00.668 --> 00:20:03.716
vi undz. undz ze'mir shoyn gevezn di letste, di shpetste.

00:20:01.174 --> 00:20:02.045
yo

00:20:03.570 --> 00:20:07.057
ver iz gek- ver iz dort nokh geven in dem lager?

00:20:05.764 --> 00:20:10.452
S.S. manen zenen gevezn. farshidene mentshn, fun Ungarn un fun Tshekhn

00:20:10.452 --> 00:20:16.071
fun farshidene. zey leyder hot men shoyn bald genumen fun Ungarn glaykh arayn in lager, in, keyn OSWIECIM.

00:20:16.071 --> 00:20:21.823
zey zenen gekumen nokh gut ongetun, mit esn ongetun. ale, zey hobn azoy vi zey zenen aropgeganen fun tsug

00:20:21.829 --> 00:20:24.078
hobn zey gemuzt ales lozn shoyn shteyn

00:20:24.078 --> 00:20:25.856
hobn gornisht gekent mitnemen.

00:20:25.862 --> 00:20:29.653
mit valizen zenen ongekumen nebekh. zey hobn gemeynt az zey forn nebekh

00:20:29.794 --> 00:20:36.962
⟨tsu undz⟩ tsu arbetn, zoln zey hobn mit tsu esn. ales hobn zey gelozt shteyn, gornisht. undz ze'mir gekumen shoyn fun lager. undz ho'mir gornisht gehat.

00:20:36.962 --> 00:20:39.932
ABER zey hobn gehat, un m'hot ales dos tsugenumen

00:20:39.932 --> 00:20:42.967
dos iz ales in di yekishe hent geganen, ales.

00:20:43.142 --> 00:20:46.477
un vos hot ir dort gemakht? ir hot dort gearbet?

00:20:45.403 --> 00:20:47.214
gornisht, gornisht gearbet.

00:20:47.074 --> 00:20:48.316
nisht gea-

00:20:47.214 --> 00:20:51.911
azoy hot zikh UNK, a gantsn tog gornisht gearbet, gedreyt zikh oyf di gas.

00:20:52.390 --> 00:20:54.443
in barak hot men nisht gemegt zayn.

00:20:52.423 --> 00:20:53.159
un

00:20:54.685 --> 00:20:59.651
vayl m'hot oyfgeroymt dem barak, hot men nisht gemegt zayn a gantsn tog UNK s'hot ge⟨UNK⟩ un s'iz ge⟨UNK⟩

00:20:59.651 --> 00:21:04.078
geregnt tsi kalt, s'hot nisht geshpilt keyn role. mir ho'mir gezitsn, gemuzt zayn in droysn.

00:21:04.253 --> 00:21:06.710
eyn mol bin ikh mikh geganen bodn

00:21:06.801 --> 00:21:10.114
nisht bodn, nor vashn, opvashn mayn kop, hob nisht gehat keyn hor

00:21:10.114 --> 00:21:12.504
nor ikh bin dokh gevezn a mentsh, hob ikh ⟨geganen⟩ opvashn

00:21:12.504 --> 00:21:15.214
hob ikh gehat di bluzke vos hob ikh getrogn, di bluz

00:21:15.214 --> 00:21:17.694
hob ikh oyfgehongen oyf dem ayzn

00:21:17.694 --> 00:21:19.894
oyf eyn mol hot men geganvet di bluz

00:21:19.894 --> 00:21:22.992
un ikh hob gedarft aroysgeyn zeks a zeyger oyf di

00:21:22.992 --> 00:21:28.469
apel plats, un di bluz iz nisht gevezn. nu, vos tut men? loyf ikh tsum barak, tsu di mame

00:21:28.469 --> 00:21:35.109
un di mame iz tsugan tsu di lager ALTESTE un hot gezogt "her tsu, m'hot zi geganvet di bluz. vos zol zi tun? zi ken dokh nisht aroysgeyn yetst.

00:21:35.109 --> 00:21:36.949
di yeke ⟨vet zi⟩ dokh bald hargenen."

00:21:36.962 --> 00:21:38.869
hot zi mir gegebn a sh- a

00:21:38.869 --> 00:21:41.490
a, fun a pizhame, fun a mener pizhame a

00:21:41.665 --> 00:21:42.756
a bluz.

00:21:43.487 --> 00:21:47.337
di mentshn zenen nisht gevezn nebekh keyn mentshn, zenen ales gevezn vi khayes.

00:21:47.337 --> 00:21:50.097
ikh vel dir zogn, ikh bin oykhet aleyn gevezn a khaye.

00:21:50.102 --> 00:21:51.631
ikh hob oykhet geshlogn.

00:21:52.296 --> 00:21:53.825
⟨vel ikh do⟩ fartseyln vayter.

00:21:54.253 --> 00:21:55.887
bin ⟨aleyn⟩ oykhet gevezn a khaye.

00:21:55.887 --> 00:21:59.413
m'hot zikh, m'hot zikh nisht gekent tsurikhaltn, vi me zogt dos do.

00:21:59.413 --> 00:22:01.520
m'hot zikh gevolt dos lebn retn.

00:22:01.543 --> 00:22:03.337
m'hot gekhapt fun yenem broyt.

00:22:03.337 --> 00:22:06.324
s'iz dokh gevezn yenem's shtikele broyt. m'hot gekhapt.

00:22:06.324 --> 00:22:11.241
m'hot gekhapt a bluze. m'hot gevolt hobn nokh a bluz, vayl zi hot dokh gehat a bluz, hot ⟨genumen⟩ nokh a bluze.

00:22:12.107 --> 00:22:15.813
m'iz gevezn nisht keyn mentshn. m'hot nisht gekent zayn keyn mentshn.

00:22:16.005 --> 00:22:18.327
m'hot gevust me geyt oyf toyt, nisht oyf lebn.

00:22:19.414 --> 00:22:21.299
vos iz epes

00:22:21.299 --> 00:22:26.189
a forfal vos es blaybt bay aykh in, fun Oyshvits, epes vos ir gedenkt?

00:22:25.827 --> 00:22:27.502
fun OSWIECIM

00:22:26.253 --> 00:22:27.542
SPEZIELL?

00:22:27.502 --> 00:22:29.330
fun OSWIECIM azoy.

00:22:29.573 --> 00:22:31.575
bin gevezn dort

00:22:33.100 --> 00:22:36.570
zenen mir arayngekumen keyn OSWIECIM

00:22:37.082 --> 00:22:39.236
na- in OSWIECIM arayn

00:22:39.495 --> 00:22:41.446
hobn mir gekrign krets

00:22:42.060 --> 00:22:43.623
oyfn gantsn kerper.

00:22:45.317 --> 00:22:46.728
ikh mit di mame.

00:22:47.123 --> 00:22:48.803
fun di kotsn

00:22:48.803 --> 00:22:51.653
tsi geshlofn mit di mentshn tsuzamen

00:22:51.653 --> 00:22:55.283
m'hot dos gekrign, ober nisht gegesn. dos ken men oykhet krign.

00:22:56.640 --> 00:22:59.722
un ze'mir gevezn azoy oysgeshit dos gants layb.

00:23:00.420 --> 00:23:02.070
di mame iz geganen tsu

00:23:02.070 --> 00:23:06.270
keyn shpitol hot men nisht gevolt geyn, vayl azoy vi iz UNK gevezn in a shpitol

00:23:06.343 --> 00:23:10.229
s'iz dort gevezn a barak, nisht keyn shpitol, nor di barak hot geheysn a shpitol

00:23:10.229 --> 00:23:16.513
az m'iz gevezn in a shpitol, hot er bald gekumen, hot er alts genumen tsu farbrenen, ts- dem zelbn tog di ale mentshn.

00:23:15.186 --> 00:23:16.310
ver?

00:23:16.705 --> 00:23:24.799
⟨di⟩ S.S. man, hot men bald aroysgenumen di ale mentshn UNK iz geganen dort, un zi hot gekukt, tsi iz dort JEMAND a bakante. zi hot getrofn a froy a bakante

00:23:25.463 --> 00:23:26.607
a doktorin.

00:23:26.607 --> 00:23:27.873
zogt zi "her tsu

00:23:27.873 --> 00:23:31.549
mayn tokhter iz oysgeshit, un ikh bin oysgeshit. vos tut men?"

00:23:32.027 --> 00:23:33.573
"kh'vel dir gebn a zakh

00:23:33.630 --> 00:23:34.535
ABER

00:23:34.693 --> 00:23:36.695
dos iz a zakh vos vet shtinken."

00:23:37.495 --> 00:23:40.054
gezogt "nem di eygenem urin

00:23:40.498 --> 00:23:46.921
un sh- va- va- vi- dos gantse layb shmir op mit di eygene urin, un gey azoy dray tog

00:23:47.991 --> 00:23:50.552
dray tog nisht vashn, nisht makhn"

00:23:50.552 --> 00:23:54.122
un m'hot azoy ⟨geme- -numen⟩. m'hot genumen di eygenem urin

00:23:54.122 --> 00:23:56.746
un m'hot zikh gevashn dos gantse kerper

00:23:56.746 --> 00:24:01.991
un azoy geganen mitn zelbn hemdele, mitn zelbn vos hobn mir gehat di pizhamen, azoy geganen

00:24:02.402 --> 00:24:06.969
un, un got zay dank, a S.S. man hot dos nisht bamerkt. keyner hot dos nisht bamerkt

00:24:07.026 --> 00:24:09.062
un ze'mir gevorn oysgeheylt.

00:24:10.958 --> 00:24:14.161
mit dem oysgeheylt. ze'mir gornisht gehat kaza ⟨min⟩ oysgeheylt.

00:24:14.161 --> 00:24:16.801
dos iz gevezn a shreklekhe tragedye.

00:24:16.801 --> 00:24:21.684
UNK far vos a tragedye? vayl tomer nemt men JEMAND shpeter tsu arbet

00:24:22.197 --> 00:24:24.117
ershte geyst a selektsye.

00:24:24.117 --> 00:24:26.848
az bist oysgeshit in gantsn

00:24:27.023 --> 00:24:29.008
vert men dokh shoyn bald tsum toyt.

00:24:30.853 --> 00:24:34.853
dos iz gevezn UNK, azoy az nokh dem hobn mir zikh stabil bahaltn

00:24:34.853 --> 00:24:38.373
biz undzer kerper hot zikh komplet klor gemakht oysge-

00:24:38.373 --> 00:24:39.490
⟨AUSGE⟩heylt

00:24:39.490 --> 00:24:42.072
vayl afile s'iz avekgeganen nor di

00:24:42.072 --> 00:24:44.611
di vo- di UNK iz ave- di

00:24:44.611 --> 00:24:50.642
di, di shtikl iz avek fun oybn, ober di krets zenen nokh alts geblibn. dos hot gedarft langzam avekgeyn in gantsn

00:24:51.660 --> 00:24:53.915
veystu di, di

00:24:54.225 --> 00:24:55.595
UNK

00:24:54.225 --> 00:24:56.227
azoy vi a flig, di, di

00:24:56.470 --> 00:24:59.680
iz, iz avekgeganen, ABER di a- iz nokh geblibn

00:24:59.680 --> 00:25:01.830
un dos iz gevezn a tragedye

00:25:01.920 --> 00:25:04.496
vayl shpeter az s'iz gekumen di

00:25:04.654 --> 00:25:06.757
iz gevezn shoyn ende

00:25:07.506 --> 00:25:10.606
⟨ot iz gekumen⟩ vider a transport undz ale tsu nemen shoyn

00:25:10.606 --> 00:25:14.016
keyn, dos hot ho- undz ho'mir nisht gevust, ABER, s'hot geheysn az

00:25:14.016 --> 00:25:15.667
m'hot shoyn undz dernokh

00:25:15.667 --> 00:25:19.647
undzer transport hot men shoyn nisht gebrengt, azoy shoyn UNK ende

00:25:19.647 --> 00:25:21.047
fir un fertsik iz gevezn

00:25:21.095 --> 00:25:24.403
undz ho'mir nisht gevust az di krig iz shoyn azoy noent iber hoypt.

00:25:24.403 --> 00:25:26.805
ver hot epes gevust? keyner hot nisht gevu-

00:25:25.410 --> 00:25:28.576
ir hot gornisht gevust vos tut zikh mitn krig.

00:25:27.047 --> 00:25:33.473
neyn, neyn. yednfal, eyn mol hobn mir gehert bombardirn vos hot, m'iz, bombardirt di tsvey krematoryum

00:25:33.473 --> 00:25:35.863
zenen gekumen di Yisroeldike PFLUGZEUGE

00:25:35.863 --> 00:25:37.823
vos zey hobn g- bombardirt di tsvey

00:25:37.823 --> 00:25:38.703
krematoryum.

00:25:38.703 --> 00:25:40.403
azoy hobn mir gornisht gevust

00:25:40.403 --> 00:25:42.428
gornisht. m'hot gelebt vi a khaye

00:25:42.428 --> 00:25:47.948
tog oys un tog ayn, tog oys un tog ayn esn un trinken un shlofn, esn un trinken un UNK

00:25:46.858 --> 00:25:53.517
m'hot gehaltn epes a, in yidishkeyt, epes a, a shabes, a epes

00:25:50.689 --> 00:25:54.513
gorni- yo, s'iz gevezn. s'iz gevezn yomkiper

00:25:54.857 --> 00:26:00.133
hot men dokh gevust az m'iz, dos hot men nokh gevust epes yomkiper, az der gantser lager hot gefast.

00:26:00.527 --> 00:26:03.896
gantse lager hot gefast, nor vos iz geven? zenen mir UNK bay nakht

00:26:04.020 --> 00:26:08.857
hobn mir gedarft nemen dos shtikele broyt, hot men dokh nisht genumen dos shtikele broyt oykhet

00:26:08.931 --> 00:26:11.011
hobn zey UNK tsugenumen dos shtikele broyt.

00:26:11.011 --> 00:26:14.241
bay tog hobn zey nisht gegebn di kave, vayl UNK nisht trinken

00:26:14.241 --> 00:26:15.201
un bay nakht

00:26:15.201 --> 00:26:18.031
mitog shtunde gevezn di zup, hobn mir oykhet nisht gegesn

00:26:18.031 --> 00:26:21.608
nor bay nakht hobn mir gehat ersht dem tsveytn tog dos shtikele broyt tsu esn

00:26:24.000 --> 00:26:26.255
ABER di gantse lager hot gefast.

00:26:27.088 --> 00:26:29.309
vi lang zenen zey dort geven?

00:26:29.164 --> 00:26:32.330
undz ze'mir dort gevezn knape dray fir monat.

00:26:32.300 --> 00:26:34.100
velkhe yor iz dos geven?

00:26:33.552 --> 00:26:35.548
dos iz gevezn fir un fertsik.

00:26:35.548 --> 00:26:39.418
biz, biz vinter tsayt zenen mir geganen keyn BERGEN BELSEN.

00:26:39.306 --> 00:26:42.219
vi hot zikh dos bashlosn, az

00:26:40.926 --> 00:26:46.086
vi UNK s'iz nokh nisht geve- vi- vider, vider gevezn, gekumen mentshn. zey hobn gedarft

00:26:46.086 --> 00:26:50.541
nisht genumen, nor zey hobn shoyn likvidirt shoyn di lager, di OSWIECIM, m'hot zi shoyn likvidirt

00:26:50.541 --> 00:26:54.268
hobn zey undz geshikt vayter keyn yeke land. dos iz BERGEN BELSEN

00:26:54.460 --> 00:26:57.744
un dort hot men undz geshikt, s'iz nisht gevezn afile keyn barakn

00:26:58.847 --> 00:27:01.591
nor s'iz gevezn, m'hot oyfgeshtelt TENTn

00:27:01.750 --> 00:27:04.174
un aroysgeyn fun p- OSWIECIM

00:27:04.618 --> 00:27:07.835
iz vider gevezn a, iz gevezn do di selektsye

00:27:07.892 --> 00:27:15.440
un do, az bist arayngeganen in UNK in a, tsu bodn zikh, un do arum un arum bistu yene zayt aroysgeganen

00:27:15.440 --> 00:27:19.124
iz di mame tsvey mol adurkhgelofn. ikh bin zi nokhgelofn

00:27:19.452 --> 00:27:21.650
un nebekh tsvey mol hot men zi tsurikgesh-

00:27:21.650 --> 00:27:23.208
-shikt di S.S. man.

00:27:22.995 --> 00:27:24.738
vu iz dos geven?

00:27:23.923 --> 00:27:25.284
in OSWIECIM.

00:27:25.203 --> 00:27:27.460
iz geven UNK selektsye?

00:27:25.594 --> 00:27:26.516
yo.

00:27:26.607 --> 00:27:30.347
bay di s- eybik ven bist aroysgeganen, bistu gan in a selektsye.

00:27:30.471 --> 00:27:33.673
tsi bist gezunt, tsi geyst in di arbet, ⟨tsi⟩ nisht bald UNK farbrenen

00:27:33.673 --> 00:27:36.081
yedes plats vu bist aroysgeganen

00:27:36.081 --> 00:27:39.678
vayl ze'mir, far vos zenen mir azoy moyre gehat? alts durkh dem vos zenen mir nokh gevezn

00:27:39.988 --> 00:27:44.876
gekretst, nisht keyn kretsn, nor s'iz nokh geblibn azolkhene flekn oyf, oyfn kerper.

00:27:44.646 --> 00:27:47.340
un vos hot dos geheysn az me shikt zi tsurik?

00:27:47.835 --> 00:27:50.465
neyn, z- vider tsurik zol zi adurkhgeyn

00:27:50.465 --> 00:27:54.235
tsu di ⟨zaln⟩, vos zey, do hot men gedarft arayngeyn vu me bodt zikh

00:27:54.332 --> 00:27:56.789
un undz ze'mir adurkhgelofn do aher

00:27:56.796 --> 00:28:01.914
un, un UNK ⟨zol men⟩ nisht adurkhgeyn di, vu me geyt dort arayn, zol men undz nisht zen

00:28:01.914 --> 00:28:03.539
az hobn mir kretser oyfn layb.

00:28:08.355 --> 00:28:09.648
dos iz ge-

00:28:08.372 --> 00:28:13.141
ABER yednfal oyf letst hot men nisht gehat keyn breyre, hobn mir dokh gemuzt arayngeyn.

00:28:13.536 --> 00:28:19.388
un dort iz gevezn a ⟨SAUM⟩ vos bret-

00:28:19.388 --> 00:28:24.735
benk, azoy vi UNK oybn aroyf, zenen mir ganen gantsn hintn, zol undz keyner nisht zen

00:28:25.416 --> 00:28:30.843
zoln mir zikh kenen dort opbodn, un ze'mir aroysgeganen, ⟨got zay dank, ze'mir⟩ ganen keyn BERGEN BELSEN.

00:28:31.255 --> 00:28:32.754
me halt zikh op do.

00:28:32.200 --> 00:28:33.142
yo, kh'hob gezen.
